queries.sql: SELECT ds1.*, ds2.id as conflict_id, ds2.start_time as conflict_start, ds2.end_time as conflict_end FROM doctor_schedules ds1 JOIN doctor_schedules ds2 ON ds1.doctor_id = ds2.doctor_id AND ds1.shift_date = ds2.shift_date AND ds1.id != ds2.id AND ds1.status != 'cancelled' AND ds2.status != 'cancelled' AND ds1.start_time < ds2.end_time AND ds1.end_time > ds2.start_time ORDER BY ds1.shift_date DESC, ds1.start_time ASC
